09:19.125 --> 09:21.571
Your eyelids are flickering,
you're lying.

09:22.061 --> 09:23.631
Yours are too.

09:23.696 --> 09:26.677
I did everything only for
the betterment of the village.

09:26.732 --> 09:28.643
- Tell her.
- He's right.

09:28.701 --> 09:30.408
This is the first time
when father taunted me..

09:30.469 --> 09:32.005
For my unemployment.

09:32.271 --> 09:33.978
