10:05.605 --> 10:07.685
Today's the last day of
admission in my son's school.

10:07.707 --> 10:09.311
And the Mayor's coming today.

10:09.375 --> 10:11.335
For the inauguration
ceremony of the African Lion.

10:11.344 --> 10:14.257
Please help me out. Please.
Of course, anything for friends.

10:14.313 --> 10:15.153
What do I have to do?

10:15.181 --> 10:18.526
You have to guard the African Lion.

10:18.751 --> 10:21.789
Mr. Lion, can you spare two minutes.
Someone wants to meet you.

10:22.355 --> 10:23.459
Here. Here.

10:23.522 --> 10:24.694
Singh... Lion!

10:26.158 --> 10:27.262
Lion... Singh!

10:28.761 --> 10:30.061
Who is it now?

10:30.062 --> 10:30.733
Oh God!

10:30.796 --> 10:31.836
I'm on my way, 15 minutes.

10:32.064 --> 10:33.236
15 minutes...

10:33.299 --> 10:35.279
The Mayor and other
bureaucrats will be attending.

10:35.334 --> 10:36.711
Just handle everything.
Lam coming.

10:36.769 --> 10:38.077
15 minutes.
- Listen.

10:38.170 --> 10:39.547
Come soon.

10:44.076 --> 10:44.781
The door is open.

10:47.346 --> 10:48.450
Mufasa!

10:50.583 --> 10:51.618
Where did he go?

10:52.084 --> 10:54.496
Mufasa! Mufasa!

10:57.323 --> 10:59.735
Hello, sir... Welcome.

10:59.792 --> 11:01.032
Oh no...

11:01.093 --> 11:02.094
Mufasa!

11:24.417 --> 11:26.328
Wonderful! Wonderful!

11:26.385 --> 11:27.659
Calm down! Calm down!

11:27.787 --> 11:31.257
Punjab, the land of Lions!

11:31.323 --> 11:33.701
And especially from Africa..

11:33.759 --> 11:38.037
We've brought a lion for you,
which will..

11:38.064 --> 11:39.771
Make you hold your breaths.

11:41.634 --> 11:43.375
Mr. Mayor, hold this.

11:44.170 --> 11:45.171
Sorry.

11:49.508 --> 11:51.784
Clap!

12:07.093 --> 12:09.039
Did the lion walk
all the way from Africa?

12:09.128 --> 12:10.436
Looks humiliating.

12:10.496 --> 12:13.272
When this lion roars...

12:13.332 --> 12:20.341
it makes people shiver.

12:20.606 --> 12:25.487
They shudder... shudder with fear.

12:25.644 --> 12:29.751
Security...
make him roar for the people.

12:33.119 --> 12:36.589
Security... tell him to roar!

12:36.655 --> 12:39.397
- Him?
- Yes, him.

12:46.565 --> 12:48.203
It's a dog!

12:48.267 --> 12:49.803
Yes...

12:52.404 --> 12:55.044
That's not a lion!

13:00.479 --> 13:03.016
You... That's a dog.

13:03.115 --> 13:05.618
I will put you in a cage.

13:05.684 --> 13:08.255
Move the cameras, what are you doing?
Who called the press here?

13:08.320 --> 13:10.163
I won't spare you.

13:10.222 --> 13:13.135
No, photographs.
I will have this dog bite you.

13:13.192 --> 13:14.398
You'll be injected..

13:14.460 --> 13:16.098
What if the lion doesn't return?

13:16.162 --> 13:18.108
I want the lion back.

13:18.597 --> 13:20.668
Hey... stop. Stop.

13:27.473 --> 13:29.146
You and your plans.

13:30.676 --> 13:34.453
The person you're trying
to call is driving at the moment.

13:34.513 --> 13:36.493
Please call next month..

13:36.549 --> 13:38.222
- Raftaar.
- Yes.

13:38.284 --> 13:39.684
I gave you such a small job to do..

13:39.718 --> 13:40.628
But you messed that up too.

13:40.686 --> 13:44.055
It wasn't my fault,
you left the cage door open.

13:44.056 --> 13:45.592
You could've closed the door.

13:45.658 --> 13:47.729
Wasn't much to do.
What is this?

13:48.160 --> 13:50.071
Do something... find the lion..

13:50.129 --> 13:51.301
And bring him before the Mayor.

13:51.363 --> 13:53.309
Where will I find him?
Just find him from anywhere..

13:53.365 --> 13:54.537
Or else I will lose my job.

13:54.600 --> 13:56.375
But I am losing mine too.

13:56.435 --> 13:57.743
I am going...

13:58.370 --> 13:59.508
Everyone's troubling me.

13:59.572 --> 14:01.552
Listen... He hung up.

14:03.108 --> 14:06.021
This must be the first
lion that cost me my job.

14:06.645 --> 14:09.251
What kind of remix is this?

14:39.111 --> 14:41.148
You dressed up a
dog to look like a lion.

14:41.213 --> 14:43.489
Isn't this misguiding
the innocent people?

14:43.549 --> 14:44.687
The country wants to know.

14:44.750 --> 14:48.197
I.. - Mr. Mayor, will you appoint
a committee to find the lion?

14:48.254 --> 14:50.325
One minute...

14:51.490 --> 14:53.436
- Hello..
- Mayor sir.

14:57.062 --> 14:58.666
How dare you come here?

14:58.731 --> 15:00.039
I warned you..

15:03.002 --> 15:05.278
Sir, I've brought him along.
What?

15:05.337 --> 15:06.213
Donkey?

15:08.173 --> 15:09.675
Lion, sir.

15:14.280 --> 15:15.088
Are you crazy?

15:15.147 --> 15:16.524
Come, Mufasa. Come.

15:19.718 --> 15:21.493
You climbed on
the table out of fear.

15:21.553 --> 15:22.623
Don't be scared, sir.

15:22.688 --> 15:25.225
He's a very tame lion,
even I was scared of him first.

15:25.291 --> 15:27.100
Why did you bring him here?

15:27.159 --> 15:31.005
Listen to me. Look at him,
he already likes you a lot.

15:31.030 --> 15:32.737
Look, he's even apologizing.

15:32.998 --> 15:34.170
He's staring at me.

15:34.233 --> 15:37.612
Mommy!
Sir, please don't fire my friend.

15:37.670 --> 15:39.206
