- I beg you...

15:53.185 --> 15:55.756
Listen to me,
even I was scared at first.

15:56.555 --> 15:58.557
He's fainted. See you.

15:58.624 --> 16:01.366
I am tying him here, keep him.

16:01.427 --> 16:02.497
Okay...

16:02.995 --> 16:03.700
Hello.

16:04.063 --> 16:05.064
See you all.

16:05.731 --> 16:07.301
Brother, listen to me.

16:07.599 --> 16:09.704
