food all day today.

16:35.361 --> 16:39.002
Save this pretence for
someone who doesn't know you two.

16:42.668 --> 16:44.670
You've never completed anything.

16:44.737 --> 16:46.216
You left your studies in between.

16:46.271 --> 16:47.872
Stopped working in
the fields in mid-way.

16:48.007 --> 16:49.281
Quit your job in the middle.

16:49.341 --> 16:51.719
But now you must
completely leave home.

16:51.777 --> 16:53.279
- Understand.
- You're right...

16:53.345 --> 16:54.653
"If you ever make
such a mistake again"

16:54.713 --> 16:56.047
you will have to leave home.

16:56.048 --> 16:58.585
No... he has to go now.

16:59.785 --> 17:01.128
What are you saying?

17:01.186 --> 17:03.097
You have only two options.

17:03.622 --> 17:06.364
Either you take up a decent
job at my friend's place in Goa.

17:06.425 --> 17:09.234
Or marry Navjot's daughter Sweety.

17:09.294 --> 17:10.465
Understand?

17:10.662 --> 17:11.696
Yes.

17:24.443 --> 17:26.616
