that's only good for wrestling.

17:32.317 --> 17:34.092
There are no options.

17:37.689 --> 17:40.431
Mom. Why are you crying?

17:40.559 --> 17:42.596
Don't you know your father?

17:43.128 --> 17:45.108
Once he's decided something...

17:45.731 --> 17:47.031
What does he want?

17:47.032 --> 17:48.306
That I should go to Goa?

17:48.634 --> 17:50.204
I'll go happily.

17:53.138 --> 17:54.708
Come on..

17:58.610 --> 18:00.089
God bless you.

18:01.346 --> 18:03.417
I hope you won't quit
this job in the middle?

18:04.450 --> 18:06.430
"You don't lack anything"

18:06.985 --> 18:08.259
except for concentration.

18:09.288 --> 18:11.427
I am not sending you
away because I've lost.

18:11.490 --> 18:13.094
I am sending you away because I know..

18:13.158 --> 18:15.229
You're capable of doing much more.

18:15.294 --> 18:17.501
And I want you to recognize yourself.

18:17.963 --> 18:20.671
If you delay,
you have a lot to lose.

18:21.500 --> 18:22.478
Understand.

18:23.235 --> 18:24.179
Now go.

18:29.108 --> 18:30.485
Welcome... son, welcome.

18:30.542 --> 18:33.022
Father, he's leaving.

19:07.179 --> 19:08.453
Hello, Mr. Rana?

19:08.981 --> 19:11.427
