20:14.646 --> 20:17.559
Mr. Nelson, you take eastern Europe.

20:17.616 --> 20:19.653
Mr. Wong, you take Asia.

20:20.018 --> 20:21.156
And you sir, Russia.

20:21.220 --> 20:22.460
Anthony, my friend.

20:22.554 --> 20:23.726
Africa's yours.

20:24.056 --> 20:25.763
This is the only
way to stop bloodshed.

20:26.024 --> 20:29.198
No loss of profit,
no loss of life.

20:35.067 --> 20:36.137
Deal.

20:36.201 --> 20:37.407
That's the spirit.

20:38.303 --> 20:39.043
