- No, no, no, dad.

23:59.237 --> 24:00.978
How can I kill you?

24:01.006 --> 24:03.111
That's why I told him to kill you.

24:03.675 --> 24:05.712
But this really pains me.

24:06.545 --> 24:08.218
But it was more painful..

24:08.280 --> 24:10.988
When you asked me to
apologies in front of everyone.

24:11.983 --> 24:14.327
You've grown old, dad.

24:14.686 --> 24:17.326
That's why you're happy
with the little you have.

24:18.623 --> 24:20.694
But I want to make it big, dad.

24:21.993 --> 24:24.200
I want total control, dad.

24:24.463 --> 24:27.569
Dad! Hey dad! Dad! Dad!

24:28.767 --> 24:30.440
It's best you die, dad.

24:30.702 --> 24:32.375
Good for you.

24:33.004 --> 24:35.314
Better for me.

24:37.409 --> 24:39.719
- Dad...
- Sir, he's dead.

24:42.647 --> 24:44.058
I'm too good.

24:52.757 --> 24:54.668
It's my time, dad.

24:58.296 --> 25:00.207
Sara, Mark has gone mad.

25:00.265 --> 25:02.211
You must leave for the US.

25:02.267 --> 25:03.473
I won't go to the US.

25:03.535 --> 25:05.674
Darling, it's only until
all this gets sorted out.

25:05.737 --> 25:07.004
You'll be safe there.

25:07.005 --> 25:09.349
Even now you want
to get rid of your problem..

25:09.407 --> 25:11.011
And not face it.

25:15.180 --> 25:16.750
I'll go wherever I want to.

25:20.252 --> 25:22.129
I know where Sara will go.

25:22.187 --> 25:23.632
Call Kirpal.

25:53.018 --> 25:55.624
I know who sent the money and why.

25:58.356 --> 26:00.632
You just rejected
500 million in 5 seconds.

26:01.059 --> 26:02.367
Such an expensive mistake.

26:02.427 --> 26:03.269
Out!

26:03.328 --> 26:06.332
Piku, that old man refused
an offer of 500 million.

26:06.398 --> 26:08.537
I wonder what the boss
is going to do with him?

26:14.239 --> 26:16.617
Hello. Wrong number.
It's just a phone.

26:18.009 --> 26:19.079
Come on.

26:19.744 --> 26:20.984
Stop.

26:21.012 --> 26:22.389
We're guest of Mr. Kirpal.

26:22.447 --> 26:23.323
Okay, hold.

26:23.381 --> 26:24.553
Sir, two men are here to see you.

26:24.616 --> 26:26.095
And one Sardar.

26:26.318 --> 26:28.264
- You mean three people.
- Yes.

26:28.320 --> 26:29.458
Send them upstairs.

26:29.521 --> 26:31.125
Send them upstairs.

26:31.356 --> 26:32.232
On the deck.

26:32.290 --> 26:34.292
I am not your father's friend.

26:34.993 --> 26:36.768
This is the address father gave me.

26:37.495 --> 26:40.032
Hey... First listen to me.

26:40.332 --> 26:43.370
I mean I am your father's friend..

26:43.435 --> 26:45.210
But out here I am your boss.

26:45.270 --> 26:46.112
Ha... Ha...

26:46.171 --> 26:47.673
- Who are these two?
- Friends.

26:47.739 --> 26:48.779
You two stand at the back.

26:49.040 --> 26:50.610
Go and stand at the back.

26:50.775 --> 26:52.755
And you...
stand at the end of this line.

26:53.011 --> 26:53.580
Yes.

26:57.215 --> 27:00.094
Do you know how much
time it takes to get her?

27:03.388 --> 27:05.061
5 seconds if I walk.

27:07.292 --> 27:08.737
And 2 seconds if I run.

27:12.998 --> 27:14.272
You must do as I say.

27:14.332 --> 27:15.709
That's what father said too.

27:15.967 --> 27:18.106
There's a rule to get
recruited here. - What?

27:18.169 --> 27:20.342
Go to that railing and jump.

27:26.678 --> 27:27.622
What did you do?

27:27.679 --> 27:29.681
Boss said
"Go to that railing and jump".

27:30.015 --> 27:31.016
And I did.

27:33.151 --> 27:35.028
'Go to that railing and jump.'

27:41.026 --> 27:41.561
He's smart!

27:48.366 --> 27:51.279
Raftaar, I'm giving
you a very important job.

27:52.103 --> 27:53.309
You need to go to Goa airport.

27:53.371 --> 27:54.145
Yes.

27:56.408 --> 27:57.113
Take this.

27:57.175 --> 27:58.381
A girl called Sara...

27:58.576 --> 28:01.216
- Singh. Where?
- Goa airport.

28:01.279 --> 28:02.656
Come back.

28:05.216 --> 28:07.127
First hear me out.

28:07.952 --> 28:09.329
You've to be at the
airport tomorrow 11 am.

28:09.387 --> 28:11.298
But there's lot of
time for that. - Yeah.

28:11.356 --> 28:12.562
Sit.

28:14.626 --> 28:16.537
Listen to me carefully, son.

28:16.961 --> 28:19.441
A girl called Sara
is arriving from Romania.

28:19.497 --> 28:20.669
She's my guest.

28:21.299 --> 28:24.610
You'll be with her
until she goes back.

28:24.669 --> 28:26.205
And take good care of her.

28:26.538 --> 28:29.451
She doesn't know Hindi,
do you know English?

28:29.507 --> 28:30.417
No.

28:32.377 --> 28:34.015
You don't know English?

28:35.113 --> 28:36.285
What are you doing here?

28:36.548 --> 28:38.152
What are you doing in Goa?
Get lost.

28:38.216 --> 28:39.593
Go back to Punjab.
Back to Punjab!

28:48.760 --> 28:49.670
Come on.

28:50.228 --> 28:51.434
Come on.

28:53.631 --> 28:54.735
I do know English.

28:54.999 --> 28:56.137
A to Z.

28:56.701 --> 28:58.044
Good.

29:00.004 --> 29:01.574
Keys to the Panjim bungalow.

29:03.341 --> 29:06.447
I'm giving you this
because I trust you.

29:06.511 --> 29:07.717
Don't worry, sir.

29:08.279 --> 29:10.452
Even I trust myself completely.

29:10.949 --> 29:11.620
Jai Hind!

29:13.051 --> 29:13.961
What a character.

29:20.959 --> 29:23.166
Hey, Singh. Get the key.

29:32.170 --> 29:33.205
Stupid.

29:33.705 --> 29:36.686
I lied... that I know English.

29:37.408 --> 29:39.183
I don't know what to do.

29:41.012 --> 29:44.186
I'll arrange for someone...
who knows Hindi and English.

29:44.249 --> 29:45.353
Don't worry.

29:45.650 --> 29:46.560
Let's go ahead.

29:46.618 --> 29:47.562
Come on.

29:58.429 --> 29:59.237
Careful.

29:59.297 --> 30:01.470
Aunty, brother Daljeet's calling.

30:01.533 --> 30:03.444
Son... how are you?

30:03.501 --> 30:05.139
Nothing's good out here, mom.

30:05.336 --> 30:07.509
Neither the food,
nor the place or the ambiance.

30:08.006 --> 30:10.008
I haven't even slept
properly since I got here.

30:10.041 --> 30:12.317
You haven't slept? Are you sick?

30:12.377 --> 30:15.017
I could never sleep
without hearing your voice.

30:16.281 --> 30:17.692
Then call me every night.

30:17.749 --> 30:19.524
I can't see your face on the phone.

30:19.584 --> 30:21.757
I maybe here,
but I'm still with you.

30:22.253 --> 30:25.063
Concentrate on your job,
and everything will be fine.

30:25.356 --> 30:27.563
Fine, mom. Take care.

30:32.597 --> 30:35.237
Raftaar, my room's really amazing.

30:39.370 --> 30:41.213
He's sad and you're dancing.

30:42.807 --> 30:44.150
Sorry, bro.

31:54.812 --> 31:56.723
- Hi.
- Hi.

32:14.032 --> 32:15.033
Now she will come.

32:15.233 --> 32:17.144
- Band.
- Let them go.

32:17.468 --> 32:18.708
Go, Go.

32:26.778 --> 32:29.258
You idiots,
you're here to receive me.

32:34.252 --> 32:36.027
Raftaar... insult.

32:36.054 --> 32:39.524
We're here to receive you,
doesn't mean we're your servants.

32:39.590 --> 32:41.399
What you did with him..

32:41.459 --> 32:43.564
If you do it again...

32:44.228 --> 32:45.707
You'll face my wrath.

32:45.763 --> 32:46.639
Yes,

32:51.069 --> 32:54.050
Raftaar, you two look
really nice together.

33:16.761 --> 33:19.571
She's a guest, not my type.

33:21.566 --> 33:23.239
This girl's got an attitude problem.

33:23.301 --> 33:25.645
I'll show her. Wear your belt.

33:27.138 --> 33:30.119
Raftaar, get ready.

34:08.212 --> 34:10.692
"You kicked me out of this Casino"

34:11.014 --> 34:12.619
and now I'm offering to buy it.

34:12.683 --> 34:15.129
And this time my offer is 750 million.

34:15.186 --> 34:18.292
I threw you out because
you got involved in drugs.

34:18.523 --> 34:21.402
And now you want to buy
my Casino with that money.

34:21.525 --> 34:23.027
You think I'll let that happen.

34:27.732 --> 34:28.472
Hey, stop.

34:29.167 --> 34:31.147
I want to meet Kirpal.
You can't.

34:31.202 --> 34:32.203
He's in a meeting with Boxer Bhai.

34:32.270 --> 34:33.510
What about him?

34:39.210 --> 34:40.313
Who's the girl?

34:40.378 --> 34:41.413
She wants to meet Kirpal.

34:41.478 --> 34:43.049
- What?
- She's from Romania.

34:43.347 --> 34:45.418
Next time there won't be an offer...

34:45.783 --> 34:47.056
I'll just help myself in.

34:47.150 --> 34:47.686
Wait.

34:54.324 --> 34:56.065
Your time is up.

34:56.594 --> 35:00.667
You should retire, go to
Canada and buy a mall or something.

35:26.524 --> 35:28.003
How is your father?

35:29.193 --> 35:30.035
Good.

35:30.394 --> 35:31.634
I thought you're
not safe in the hotel..

35:31.696 --> 35:33.403
So I put you in my bungalow.

35:34.599 --> 35:35.543
Thank you.

35:36.400 --> 35:38.676
If you have any problem,
you can tell Singh.

35:43.474 --> 35:45.613
Don't worry,
I'll take care of myself.

35:46.144 --> 35:48.454
He may be silly but
he's very dependable.

36:09.567 --> 36:10.739
Insulted again.

36:15.373 --> 36:16.716
That's our bag!

36:19.710 --> 36:22.691
Stop. Stop the car.

36:25.516 --> 36:27.189
This is your room.

36:27.251 --> 36:30.425
It's got a balcony..
Cupboard...

36:30.488 --> 36:31.694
Bathroom...

36:35.726 --> 36:37.706
Did you show her, her room?

36:38.196 --> 36:39.607
She's got an attitude.

36:39.664 --> 36:41.371
Keep her away from me.

36:41.999 --> 36:42.534
Hey...

36:44.435 --> 36:45.675
Your room's that way.

36:45.736 --> 36:47.443
What are you doing here?
Raftaar.

36:49.740 --> 36:51.276
That girl left her room..

36:52.043 --> 36:53.147
She's here.

36:53.778 --> 36:56.019
Open the door,
don't make me mad.

36:56.214 --> 36:57.056
See.

36:58.583 --> 36:59.493
See.

36:59.717 --> 37:00.991
I'll show her.

37:08.693 --> 37:11.503
Why does my future seem
in the dark?

37:14.432 --> 37:16.605
This girl isn't
taking us seriously.

37:16.667 --> 37:18.146
I'll show her.

37:22.506 --> 37:25.749
Stop the truck. My bag.

37:26.010 --> 37:27.683
Stop.

37:47.665 --> 37:52.205
Sir, Sara has left Romania..

37:52.270 --> 37:54.716
And nobody knows which
part of the world she's in.

37:54.772 --> 37:56.445
That's good news.

37:56.507 --> 37:57.383
You know...

37:57.441 --> 38:02.049
If she had been here,
I would've caught her and killed her.

38:02.346 --> 38:03.381
Finish!

38:04.248 --> 38:05.625
No glamour.

38:05.983 --> 38:08.361
Easy is boring man.

38:12.423 --> 38:15.302
She'll hide and I'll find her.

38:15.660 --> 38:18.607
She'll run and I'll hunt her.

38:21.365 --> 38:22.309
I like it.

38:31.142 --> 38:33.349
This is an old way
to show-off your brawn.

38:33.978 --> 38:35.252
But it's effective.

38:37.448 --> 38:38.085
Come on.

38:45.523 --> 38:48.732
You and you...
scream when I say.

38:48.993 --> 38:50.370
- Get it.
- Yes.

39:08.546 --> 39:09.991
She's coming.

39:10.081 --> 39:11.321
And now...

39:11.382 --> 39:12.622
Hit me.

39:12.683 --> 39:14.390
Wait... that's the fake one, right?

39:14.452 --> 39:15.226
Yes, it's fake.

39:15.286 --> 39:16.629
That's the real one.

39:17.188 --> 39:18.360
That's the real one. Okay.

39:19.290 --> 39:20.098
Hit me.

39:38.743 --> 39:40.188
Now it's my turn.

39:40.544 --> 39:43.024
Come here, and turn around.

39:51.222 --> 39:52.758
Be strong. Be strong.

40:13.377 --> 40:16.153
I was here for the
job of a translator.

40:16.213 --> 40:17.453
I guess I am at the wrong address.

40:17.515 --> 40:18.118
Hey!

40:18.182 --> 40:19.684
Hey specky, come here.

40:22.486 --> 40:25.729
Drink Rasna...
it'll cool your mind.

40:35.766 --> 40:36.710
It's cool.

40:37.501 --> 40:38.479
Bye!

40:42.540 --> 40:43.746
Hi.

40:43.808 --> 40:45.253
What's your name?

40:45.309 --> 40:46.219
Emily.

40:47.211 --> 40:48.281
Imli?

40:49.680 --> 40:51.318
That's a tart name.

40:52.683 --> 40:54.685
Ask her...
what's she doing in Goa?

40:55.653 --> 40:57.155
Why have you come to Goa?

40:57.221 --> 40:59.064
It's none of his business.

40:59.089 --> 41:01.296
'She'll get herself
killed and me too.'

41:03.561 --> 41:07.509
She... likes to see new places,
eat new food..

41:07.565 --> 41:10.011
And make new friends.

41:10.034 --> 41:11.513
She's here to make friends.

41:12.369 --> 41:14.280
Does she know all of us?

41:15.105 --> 41:16.641
Do you know who they are?

41:19.310 --> 41:22.223
Morons! Three morons.

41:24.482 --> 41:27.691
Great... great people.

41:30.554 --> 41:32.431
The idea's working.

41:32.490 --> 41:33.730
Did she understand?
Do you want to call the cops?

41:33.791 --> 41:37.705
Hey... don't try to get too friendly.

41:37.761 --> 41:40.708
Tell her... if she needs
to get anything done in Goa..

41:40.764 --> 41:42.766
Then speak to me.

41:49.073 --> 41:50.051
Let's go.

41:51.208 --> 41:55.088
If you want anything done...
he can do anything in Goa.

42:00.584 --> 42:02.393
But what do we
do with this woman?

42:02.586 --> 42:06.500
She wants you to help
her find this woman.

42:07.224 --> 42:09.500
Tell her not to worry,
it'll be clone.

42:09.560 --> 42:10.504
Tell her.

42:11.028 --> 42:13.338
He said don't worry...
he will help you find her.

42:13.764 --> 42:14.572
<i>Pappi.</i>

42:15.533 --> 42:16.443
Take a look.

42:18.002 --> 42:18.707
Show him as well.

42:20.471 --> 42:23.008
You will have to worry
if you don't find her.

42:23.741 --> 42:25.243
I will break your bones.

42:33.017 --> 42:35.520
She has faith in
your strong shoulders.

42:40.024 --> 42:41.196
- Raftaar!
- Raftaar!

42:43.427 --> 42:46.271
What? - We're hungry,
how about we get something to eat.

42:49.199 --> 42:51.577
She said... she likes
to see new places.

42:52.703 --> 42:54.546
Let's take her out,
let's eat out.

42:54.605 --> 42:55.413
- Yes.
- Let's go.

43:11.121 --> 43:12.998
Why the hell
is he blushing so much?

43:13.624 --> 43:14.762
What did she say?

43:15.259 --> 43:19.571
She's saying you've got
the best smile she's ever seen.

43:22.199 --> 43:24.236
Got her! Got her! Got her!

43:29.440 --> 43:31.442
Tell her she's very beautiful.

43:31.508 --> 43:33.181
Jesus, what did you get me into?

43:33.243 --> 43:35.154
Come on... tell her now.
Tell her...

43:36.513 --> 43:40.017
Tell her.
He says you're very beautiful.

43:42.686 --> 43:46.224
If he flirts with me...
I will kick him.

43:53.564 --> 43:54.634
What did she say?

43:55.366 --> 43:57.710
She expects a lot from you.

43:58.168 --> 44:00.045
She's got great hopes.

44:01.972 --> 44:03.178
A

44:04.174 --> 44:05.209
Hope.

44:07.011 --> 44:08.490
Have you got money?

44:08.545 --> 44:10.149
I didn't bring my purse.

44:10.214 --> 44:11.318
Raftaar's got...

44:11.382 --> 44:13.384
Raftaar! Raftaar!

44:13.450 --> 44:14.520
Raftaar!

44:14.585 --> 44:16.258
- Raftaar!
- Raftaar!

44:17.221 --> 44:18.427
He's lost in his dreams again.

44:18.489 --> 44:20.662
Let's follow him
and take Imli along.

44:20.724 --> 44:22.328
What? Why?

44:22.393 --> 44:24.498
You'll explain Raftaar's song to Sara.

44:24.561 --> 44:25.539
Come on.

44:25.596 --> 44:26.472
"Beat!"

44:32.770 --> 44:33.714
"Banjo."

44:40.110 --> 44:41.054
"Sing."

44:46.183 --> 44:48.163
"Singh... Sing."

44:48.218 --> 44:52.030
"Baby your love's
completely floored me."

44:52.056 --> 44:55.367
"Don't make me wait too long."

44:59.063 --> 45:02.442
"After locking my eyes with yours."

45:02.499 --> 45:06.174
"I've entered the game of love."

45:06.236 --> 45:09.376
"He wants to say...
that he loves you well."

45:09.440 --> 45:13.252
"Now you got to tell
him something too."

45:13.310 --> 45:16.587
"In every way,
I just want to say."

45:16.647 --> 45:20.288
"That you are the one,
baby I love you."

45:20.350 --> 45:23.024
"Hearing you agree..."

45:23.120 --> 45:24.190
"My heart goes..."

