"My heart says..."

45:59.223 --> 45:59.792
"Bro..."

46:00.023 --> 46:03.163
"You seem like an angel to me."

46:03.227 --> 46:07.004
"Your voice casts a spell on me."

46:10.434 --> 46:13.745
"I just see an angel baby,
whenever I look at you."

46:13.971 --> 46:17.544
"When I hear your magic
it's making me crazy too."

46:17.608 --> 46:21.613
"I'm going to hold
you tight in my arms."

46:21.678 --> 46:25.216
"Just keep staring
at me with a smile."

46:25.282 --> 46:28.024
