"My heart goes..."

46:49.473 --> 46:50.611
"Let it go.."

46:51.308 --> 46:52.286
"Let it go.."

46:52.342 --> 46:55.050
"Sway to the beat
and lets sing and dance."

46:55.112 --> 46:56.022
"Let it go.."

46:56.647 --> 46:57.591
"Let it go.."

46:58.582 --> 46:59.526
"Let it go.."

46:59.583 --> 47:01.290
"Sway to the beat and.."

47:01.351 --> 47:02.056
"Don't stop."

47:02.119 --> 47:02.688
"Let it go.."

