47:06.190 --> 47:07.999
"Bro... take it slow."

47:08.058 --> 47:11.403
"My queen,
this is the grandeur of your king."

47:11.461 --> 47:15.409
"Only you look good alongside
this handsome Singh."

47:18.702 --> 47:20.409
"I'm your king,
and you're my queen.."

47:20.470 --> 47:22.381
"..and that's the
way it's supposed to be."

47:22.439 --> 47:24.009
"Now you're standing
with your Singh.."

47:24.107 --> 47:26.178
"..because you look
best when you're with me."

47:26.610 --> 47:30.114
"With your beautiful
face dwelling in my eyes."

47:30.180 --> 47:33.252
<i>"I'll</i> drench you in
the color of my love."

47:33.317 --> 47:36.298
"Your intoxication
gets me high.."

47:36.353 --> 47:37.491
"My heart goes..."

