"My heart goes..."

47:54.271 --> 47:55.375
"My heart goes..."

48:04.581 --> 48:07.391
Aunty, brother Daljeet's calling.

48:09.052 --> 48:11.532
How are you?
Fine, mom. How about you?

48:11.588 --> 48:13.124
You sound really happy.

48:13.190 --> 48:14.533
That's Goa, mom.

48:14.591 --> 48:16.002
It's a wonderful place.

48:16.059 --> 48:17.663
Different dawn, different evening..

48:17.728 --> 48:19.674
Different food, different people.

48:19.730 --> 48:21.368
Everything. I'm having fun.

48:21.431 --> 48:23.001
- Who's the girl?
- Sara.

48:23.100 --> 48:23.635
Huh?

48:23.700 --> 48:26.681
Mom, don't you have
anything better to do?

48:26.970 --> 48:29.541
I'm here to work,
not to stare at girls.

48:29.606 --> 48:31.085
I'm your mom.

48:31.141 --> 48:33.417
You're away from my sights,
but not my thoughts.

48:33.477 --> 48:34.649
Amazing, mom.

48:34.711 --> 48:36.452
I can never hide
anything from you.

48:43.420 --> 48:45.400
Nor does she hide anything.

48:49.259 --> 48:52.035
Listen... send me
a picture immediately.

48:52.095 --> 48:55.406
My picture.
The girl. I mean you two together.

48:55.465 --> 48:56.500
Yes, I will.

49:11.481 --> 49:13.085
"My heart goes..."

