"My heart goes..."

49:54.024 --> 49:55.002
Oh!

49:59.096 --> 50:00.734
The food and music here is nice.

50:00.998 --> 50:01.635
Tell her.

50:01.698 --> 50:04.008
This place has superb food and music.

50:04.034 --> 50:07.140
Stop, stop... where are you going?
Let go.

50:07.204 --> 50:09.480
Let's have fun,
let's eat and drink.

50:09.539 --> 50:11.018
Stop.

50:11.041 --> 50:12.042
Let me go.

50:12.142 --> 50:14.144
It's a moonlit night.
I'll call the police.

