get us married.

01:48:12.555 --> 01:48:13.556
Mark!

01:48:13.623 --> 01:48:16.194
Don't even dare!

01:48:22.966 --> 01:48:26.106
You have 48 hours to
say 'yes' for our marriage.

01:48:28.071 --> 01:48:30.574
